results.name: Denominators of resistance values < 1 ohm that can be obtained from a network of exactly 6 one-ohm resistors, but not from any network with fewer than 6 one-ohm resistors. Numerators are in A338580.
example: The list of the 44 = A338197(6) resistance values, sorted by increasing size of R = A338580(n)/a(n) = A338606(n)/A338600(6), is the union of [1/6, 2/9, 3/11, ..., 11/13, 9/10, 10/11] and of the corresponding reciprocal resistances > 1 ohm [11/10, 10/9, 13/11, ..., 11/3, 9/2, 6].
